d from heaven to people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The covenant of faithfulness descended from the heavens and settled in the hearts of men. The Quran was revealed and they read it in the Quran and learned it from the Sunnah.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6848, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15684,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/14\/reciting-juz-quran-at-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":25891,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Juz: Reciting a part of the Quran nightly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever falls asleep and forgets to recite his portion of the Quran, or a part of it, if he recites it between the dawn and noon prayers it will be recorded as if he recited\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19212,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/21\/ikhlaas-1-3-kafirun-1-4\/","url_meta":{"origin":25891,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Ikhlas is one-third, al-Kafirun is one-forth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The M